    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const j = $json;\nconst fmt$ = (n) => n ? '$' + Number(n).toLocaleString() : 'Unknown';\n\nconst prompt = `You are a strategic account planner using Backstory (People.ai) signal data.\n\nAccount: ${j.accountName}\nAnchor Opportunity: ${j.opportunityName} (${fmt$(j.opportunityAmount)}, owner: ${j.opportunityOwner})\n\n## Account Status\n${j.accountStatus}\n\n## Recent Account Activity\n${j.recentActivity}\n\n## Engaged Stakeholders\n${j.engagedPeople}\n\n## Comparable Account Expansion Plays (Situation Search)\n${j.situationSearch}\n\nProduce a Slack-formatted account plan brief:\n\n:clipboard: *Account Plan — ${j.accountName}*\n\n*Account Snapshot* — health, momentum, key risks\n\n*Recent Activity Summary* — what happened in the last 30 days\n\n*Strategic Priorities* — top 2-3 focus areas\n\n*Similar Account Plays* — 2-3 comparable accounts and what worked\n\n*Recommended Next Steps* — 3 specific actions for the account team this week\n\nBe direct. Use Slack mrkdwn (*bold*, • bullets).`;\n\nreturn [{ json: { ...j, prompt } }];"
      },
